* {{rhymes|en|ɪf|s=1}}
===Interjection===
{{en-interj}}
# {{lb|en|onomatopoeic|apocryphal}} Representing the [[bark]] of a [[fox]] (especially while mating).
# {{lb|en|of a person|informal}} To express happiness, to state that something is sexy.
===Noun===
{{en-noun|-|s}}
{{wikipedia|Yiff}}
# {{lb|en|slang|informal}} Sex, especially between [[furry|furries]] (fictional [[anthropomorphic]] animal characters, and/or members of the community surrounding their celebration).
#: "FurryMuck '''yiffs''' are like real-life '''yiffs''' - there is a time and place for everything." &mdash; [http://groups-beta.google.com/group/alt.fan.furry/msg/4e094a46fba477cd]
# {{lb|en|slang|informal}} Pornography of or involving furries.
#:''Do you draw '''yiff'''?''
